collections.name: Exploration of the Ether
collections.description:

Each piece is a portal into the infinite, capturing the fluidity of energy, the interwoven networks of thought and nature, and the boundless potential of light itself as it traverses dimensions.

This collection merges psychedelic surrealism, sacred geometry, and cosmic exploration, creating a journey beyond the tangible—into the ether. Are these glimpses of neural pathways? “Exploration of the Ether” invites collectors to own a fragment of the unseen, forever minted on the blockchain.

collections.name: Dream Quest
collections.description:
"Why do I dream?"
A simple question led me into an infinite world.
Perhaps the dreams we have are nothing more than a game—
A stage built from forgotten emotions, unspoken desires,
fears, and hopes, woven together like tiny pixels.

Persephina embarks on a journey to find her dreams.
But what she seeks is more than just fragments of memories.
Her quest is about collecting lost pieces of dreams,
but what awaits her at the end of this journey?

This NFT collection brings Persephina’s dreamworld to life through 8-bit pixel art.
Collectors become explorers, each holding a fragment of a dream.
Step into Persephina’s world and embark on this adventure to rediscover the dreams once lost.

collections.name: Spacebots
collections.description:
Spacebot Crew: Guardians of the Cosmos

The Spacebot Crew is an elite team of autonomous explorers, engineers, and scientists built for deep-space missions. Designed for adaptability and efficiency, each member has a specialized role that ensures the success of intergalactic operations—from asteroid mining to first contact with alien civilizations.

Equipped with cutting-edge AI and self-repairing exo-frames, the Spacebot Crew ventures into the unknown, navigating cosmic anomalies, deciphering alien transmissions, and maintaining the integrity of their starship. Whether piloting through treacherous wormholes, analyzing new planetary ecosystems, or defending against spaceborne threats, these bots are the ultimate pioneers of the final frontier.

Bound by logic yet driven by curiosity, the Spacebot Crew’s primary mission is to explore, innovate, and safeguard the galaxy for future generations—one star system at a time. 🚀✨
